of space and time.

00:13:29.060 --> 00:13:32.180 align:middle line:84%
And that is what is a
fixed law of the universe,

00:13:32.180 --> 00:13:35.350 align:middle line:84%
that space and time
are always created

00:13:35.350 --> 00:13:40.340 align:middle line:84%
in the ratio 186,000 miles of
space for every second of time.

00:13:40.340 --> 00:13:42.040 align:middle line:90%
And that is what is constant.

00:13:42.040 --> 00:13:44.320 align:middle line:90%
So it's not a constant speed.

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:46.540 align:middle line:84%
It appears to us as
a constant speed.

00:13:46.540 --> 00:13:48.970 align:middle line:84%
It's actually a constant
ratio of creation.

00:13:48.970 --> 00:13:50.180 align:middle line:90%
>> The space-time ratio.

00:13:50.180 --> 00:13:50.980 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:13:50.980 --> 00:13:53.063 align:middle line:84%
And Einstein was onto that,
because he was saying,

00:13:53.063 --> 00:13:54.280 align:middle line:90%
underneath is the space--

00:13:54.280 --> 00:13:57.420 align:middle line:84%
the real reality is the
space-time continuum,

00:13:57.420 --> 00:14:01.840 align:middle line:84%
out of which emerge the
