00:14:01.840 --> 00:14:04.630 align:middle line:84%
And the experience
of space and time

00:14:04.630 --> 00:14:07.960 align:middle line:84%
always emerge in
that fixed ratio.

00:14:07.960 --> 00:14:11.320 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, you also suggest
that light is related

00:14:11.320 --> 00:14:14.040 align:middle line:90%
to consciousness.

00:14:14.040 --> 00:14:16.180 align:middle line:84%
One might, say
since light is just

00:14:16.180 --> 00:14:19.660 align:middle line:84%
about the most fundamental
