00:14:19.660 --> 00:14:22.610 align:middle line:84%
in physics, that if light is
associated with consciousness,

00:14:22.610 --> 00:14:25.370 align:middle line:84%
then consciousness
permeates everything.

00:14:25.370 --> 00:14:26.170 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:14:26.170 --> 00:14:29.800 align:middle line:84%
Well, what I was saying was
that the light of physics

00:14:29.800 --> 00:14:32.335 align:middle line:84%
bears very, very, very
close similarities

00:14:32.335 --> 00:14:33.700 align:middle line:90%
to the light of consciousness.

00:14:33.700 --> 00:14:35.920 align:middle line:84%
And I think they are
indicative of a far

00:14:35.920 --> 00:14:37.990 align:middle line:84%
more profound connection
than we realize.

00:14:37.990 --> 00:14:40.150 align:middle line:84%
I'm not saying they're
the same thing.

00:14:40.150 --> 00:14:41.920 align:middle line:84%
But just as light
is everywhere, I

00:14:41.920 --> 00:14:43.870 align:middle line:84%
believe consciousness
is everywhere.

00:14:43.870 --> 00:14:47.030 align:middle line:84%
I don't think consciousness
evolved at a certain stage

00:14:47.030 --> 00:14:47.830 align:middle line:90%
of evolution.

00:14:47.830 --> 00:14:50.500 align:middle line:84%
I think dogs and things
are clearly conscious.

00:14:50.500 --> 00:14:52.120 align:middle line:90%
They have experiences.

00:14:52.120 --> 00:14:54.640 align:middle line:84%
I think as you go down
the evolutionary tree,

00:14:54.640 --> 00:14:57.130 align:middle line:84%
the consciousness may
get dimmer and dimmer.

00:14:57.130 --> 00:14:59.660 align:middle line:84%
But I don't think there's
any point where it started.

00:14:59.660 --> 00:15:01.690 align:middle line:84%
I think it goes all
the way down, just gets

00:15:01.690 --> 00:15:04.870 align:middle line:84%
fainter and fainter and fainter
and fainter and fainter.

00:15:04.870 --> 00:15:08.260 align:middle line:84%
But I believe that consciousness
is fundamental to the universe

00:15:08.260 --> 00:15:10.180 align:middle line:90%
and is in everything.

00:15:10.180 --> 00:15:12.100 align:middle line:90%
It is everything.

00:15:12.100 --> 00:15:14.770 align:middle line:84%
But only when the
physical world has

00:15:14.770 --> 00:15:17.350 align:middle line:84%
evolved to the sort of
qualities that we have,

00:15:17.350 --> 00:15:20.740 align:middle line:84%
the complexities that we
have, does consciousness

00:15:20.740 --> 00:15:23.590 align:middle line:84%
evolve to take on the
very complex forms

00:15:23.590 --> 00:15:25.600 align:middle line:84%
that we experience
in our own minds.

00:15:25.600 --> 00:15:29.170 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, in the first interview
