00:15:29.170 --> 00:15:32.800 align:middle line:84%
you referred to consciousness
as if it were a movie projector

00:15:32.800 --> 00:15:34.630 align:middle line:90%
without any film in it.

00:15:34.630 --> 00:15:35.440 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:15:35.440 --> 00:15:37.840 align:middle line:84%
Well, the normal mind is
the image on the screen.

00:15:37.840 --> 00:15:41.290 align:middle line:84%
Pure consciousness is like
the light behind the film.

00:15:41.290 --> 00:15:43.180 align:middle line:84%
So consciousness
is the light that

00:15:43.180 --> 00:15:44.890 align:middle line:84%
is shining in the
mind, which takes

00:15:44.890 --> 00:15:49.860 align:middle line:84%
on all the different forms and
qualities of our experience.

00:15:49.860 --> 00:15:52.960 align:middle line:84%
>> Now, the mystics have
referred to consciousness this

00:15:52.960 --> 00:15:54.590 align:middle line:90%
way in most traditions.

00:15:54.590 --> 00:15:55.390 align:middle line:90%
>> Yes.

00:15:55.390 --> 00:15:56.640 align:middle line:90%
And that's what's interesting.

00:15:56.640 --> 00:16:00.490 align:middle line:84%
Around the world, you see very,
very similar descriptions.

00:16:00.490 --> 00:16:02.810 align:middle line:84%
And these are people who've
explored consciousness

00:16:02.810 --> 00:16:03.610 align:middle line:90%
firsthand.

00:16:03.610 --> 00:16:04.060 align:middle line:90%
They're mystics.

00:16:04.060 --> 00:16:06.280 align:middle line:84%
They're basically people
who through meditation

00:16:06.280 --> 00:16:08.800 align:middle line:84%
or other forms of
internal practice

00:16:08.800 --> 00:16:11.570 align:middle line:84%
have looked at the nature of
consciousness in their mind.

00:16:11.570 --> 00:16:13.810 align:middle line:84%
They haven't gone out
