00:16:13.810 --> 00:16:15.430 align:middle line:84%
by studying people's
brainwaves, which

00:16:15.430 --> 00:16:16.480 align:middle line:90%
is what science does today.

00:16:16.480 --> 00:16:17.920 align:middle line:84%
They've gone inside,
which I think

00:16:17.920 --> 00:16:20.620 align:middle line:84%
is the real laboratory
of consciousness,

00:16:20.620 --> 00:16:25.090 align:middle line:84%
and explored their own
processes in incredible depth.

00:16:25.090 --> 00:16:27.150 align:middle line:84%
And from that comes the
various conclusions.

00:16:27.150 --> 00:16:30.730 align:middle line:84%
And one of these is that
everything is a manifestation

00:16:30.730 --> 00:16:31.620 align:middle line:90%
of consciousness.

00:16:31.620 --> 00:16:36.560 align:middle line:84%
>> So that there is a sense
in which the whole universe,

00:16:36.560 --> 00:16:38.480 align:middle line:90%
the whole universe is within us.

00:16:38.480 --> 00:16:39.280 align:middle line:90%
>> Exactly.

00:16:39.280 --> 00:16:40.930 align:middle line:84%
And this many of
these people say.

00:16:40.930 --> 00:16:43.180 align:middle line:84%
If you read their
descriptions, they talk about,

00:16:43.180 --> 00:16:44.200 align:middle line:90%
I am the universe.

00:16:44.200 --> 00:16:45.250 align:middle line:90%
I am the stars.

00:16:45.250 --> 00:16:47.770 align:middle line:84%
The whole world
revolves within me.

00:16:47.770 --> 00:16:49.212 align:middle line:90%
Now, we try and understand that.

00:16:49.212 --> 00:16:51.670 align:middle line:84%
We think, well, that's either
a very egotistical statement,

00:16:51.670 --> 00:16:54.040 align:middle line:84%
or they're having some
delusion that they are--

00:16:54.040 --> 00:16:55.720 align:middle line:90%
the whole universe is in them.

00:16:55.720 --> 00:17:00.160 align:middle line:84%
They are not talking about the
physical universe as this thing

00:17:00.160 --> 00:17:01.090 align:middle line:90%
out here.

00:17:01.090 --> 00:17:04.849 align:middle line:84%
What they are talking about is
the universe as they know it.

00:17:04.849 --> 00:17:09.349 align:middle line:84%
Everything in the known universe
